				\begin{document}$$m_\text {basal}, m_\text {size}, m_\text {div}$$\end{document}mbasal,msize,mdiv and other properties. Therefore, we allow the rates of the processes to depend on individual-specific, potential time-dependent covariates \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
