The models we use in this work are examples of concrete model parameterisations. Yet, they still inherit some simplifying assumptions limiting their applicability in practice. In addition to the assumptions made in Sect. 2, we only applied them to simulated data, which allowed some simplifying assumptions on the initial point \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
